# Google Drive OAuth Client ID (required for Cloud Backup)
# Get this from Google Cloud Console → APIs & Services → Credentials
# App type: Chrome Extension. Use the extension's Item ID as the Application ID.
# Create separate client IDs for development and production builds.
# Copy this file to .env.development and .env.production with real values.
# Never commit real client IDs — those files are gitignored.
VITE_GOOGLE_DRIVE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_drive_oauth_client_id_here
